<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-9049] Websocket Component not shutting down embedded jetty server on component shutdown</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-9049</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When stopping the websocket component, it has been observed that the embedded Jetty server does not completely shut down. This causes a bind error when attempting to start the component again. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12851423">CAMEL-9049</key>
